Load configuration from a dictionary structured as follows:
{
    "general": {
        "verbosity": 1,
        "max_cycles": 100,
        "input": "input.xyz"
    },
    "xtb": {
        "xtb_option": "opt"
    },
    "orca": {
        "orca_option": "opt"
    }
}

Arguments:
    config_dict (dict): Dictionary containing the configuration
